File Structure
main() – Runs the program: creates, prints, modifies, and prints again.

create_mat() – Allocates and fills the initial random matrix.

print() – Displays the matrix on the console.

modifate_matrix() – Loops over cells to apply the transformation.

check_and_change() – Checks neighbor mines and updates cell values.

Compilation & Run
