Notes
SIZE is defined at the top of the file (#define SIZE 5), change this value to use a larger/smaller grid.

Current implementation modifies the matrix in place, so counts may be affected if updated cells are processed before others.

If you want accurate counts without interference, store updates in a temporary matrix and copy back after all calculations.
